### ───────────────────────────────────────────────
### COURSES
### ───────────────────────────────────────────────

### Create a course
POST http://localhost:5000/api/courses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "COEN 352",
  "name": "Data Structures and Algorithms",
  "semester": "Fall 2026",
  "targetHours": 5
}

### List all courses
GET http://localhost:5000/api/courses


### ───────────────────────────────────────────────
### TASKS
### ───────────────────────────────────────────────

### Create a task — REPLACE COURSE_ID with a real id from the response above
POST http://localhost:5000/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "courseId": "69ec23c47f80684c248e5eee",
  "type": "assignment",
  "title": "Assignment 3: Hash Tables",
  "estimatedHours": 4,
  "status": "not-started"
}

### List all tasks
GET http://localhost:5000/api/tasks

### List tasks for a specific course — REPLACE COURSE_ID
GET http://localhost:5000/api/tasks?courseId=COURSE_ID


### ───────────────────────────────────────────────
### SESSIONS
### ───────────────────────────────────────────────

### Create a session linked to a course — REPLACE COURSE_ID
POST http://localhost:5000/api/sessions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "courseId": "69ec23c47f80684c248e5eee",
  "duration": 90,
  "topics": "Hash table chaining vs open addressing",
  "productivity": 4
}

### List all sessions
GET http://localhost:5000/api/sessions

### List sessions for a specific course — REPLACE COURSE_ID
GET http://localhost:5000/api/sessions?courseId=COURSE_ID